
@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Forum";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/HomePage.cshtml";
}
<script src="~/Scripts/readMoreJS.min.js" ></script>
<style>
    .subheads {
        height:100px;
    }
    .offer-forum {
        background-image: url(../Upload/bg/bestbg.jpg);
        background-size:cover;
        background-attachment:fixed;
        background-position-y:bottom;
        clip-path: polygon(0 0, 50% 22%, 100% 0, 100% 100%, 50% 78%, 0 100%);
        height: 500px;
    }
    .head-forum {
        width:100%;
        height:100%;
        text-align:center;
        font-weight:bolder;
        font-size:40px;
        padding:150px 0px 50px 0px;
        color:#808080;
    }
    .newfeed-cover {
        width:100%;
        box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        position:relative;
        border-radius:5px;
        margin-bottom:20px;
    }
    .avatar {
        width:100%;
        padding:20px;
    }
    .avatar img {
        width: 80px;
        height: 80px;
        border-radius:50%;
    }
    .name {
        font-size:20px;
        font-weight:bolder;
        padding-top:20px;
        padding-left:20px;
    }
    .content-newfeed {
        padding:20px;
    }
    .pic img {
        height: auto;
        width: 100%;
    }
    
    .action {
        height: 50px;
    }
    .action .col {
        text-align: center;
    }
    .action .like button{
        padding-top: 5px;
        background-color:transparent;
        font-size:30px;
        border:none;
        outline:none;
        cursor:pointer;
    }
    .action .like button:active {
        transform:scale(0.95);
    }
    .action .comment button{
        
        padding-top: 5px;
        background-color:transparent;
        font-size:30px;
        border:none;
        outline:none;
        cursor:pointer;
    }
    .action .comment button:active {
        transform:scale(0.95);
    }
    .comment-box {
        padding:20px;
        height:100px;
    }
    .text-comment {
        width:100%;
    }
    .text-comment form {
        height: 40px;
        width: 100%;
        background: none;
        display: flex;
    }
    .text-comment form input {
        height:100%;
        width:100%;
        background:none;
        border:none;
        outline:none;
        padding-left:30px;
        font-size:18px;
        font-weight:bold;  
        background:#dedede;
        color:#808080;
        border-radius:50px;

    }
    .text-comment .avatar-sm img{
        height:40px;
        width:40px;
        margin-right:5px;
        border-radius:50%;
    }
    ::-webkit-input-placeholder {
        color:#808080;
    }
    .text-comment button {
        width:50px;
        border:none;
        outline:none;
        background-color:transparent;
        cursor:pointer;

    }
    .text-comment button:active {
        transform:scale(0.95);
    }
    .text-comment button i {
        font-size:35px;
        color:#eeba10;
    }
    .comment-gene {
        padding-left: 40px;
        padding-right:40px;
    }
    .comment-gene .message-box {
        padding:20px;
        background:#dedede;
        border-radius:10px;
        margin-bottom:10px;
        margin-top:5px;
    }
    .comment-gene .avatar-sm-usr img {
        height:40px;
        width:40px;
        margin-right:5px;
        border-radius:50%;
    }
    .comment-gene {
        font-weight:bold;
        font-size:16px;
        color:#808080;
    }
    .LoadMore4 {
        padding:10px;
        border:none;
        outline:none;
        background:none;
        cursor:pointer;
        font-size:20px;
    }
    .LoadMore4:hover {
        color:#808080;
    }
    .items4 {
        display:none;
    }
    
</style>
<div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="row subheads"></div>
    <div class="row offer-forum">
        <div class="head-forum">
            Forum <br />
            The place to answer all your questions
        </div>
    </div>
    @*vong lap bai viet*@
    <div class="container newfeed-cover">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="avatar col"><img src="~/Upload/Team/Hung.jpg" alt="Alternate Text" /><span class="name">Name</span></div> @*Admin img*@
        </div>
        <div class="row content-newfeed dummy">
            <p>Morbi vehicula tellus non vestibulum aliquet. Etiam viverra nulla justo, in convallis mauris dictum ut. Duis ac elit vel purus mattis pellentesque ut vel magna. Pellentesque iaculis dui sit amet justo lobortis, sit amet porta diam gravida. Sed dolor nibh, facilisis in ligula sit amet, vestibulum convallis mauris. In vitae elementum dolor, egestas ornare neque. Fusce sit amet turpis tincidunt, interdum lorem vitae, accumsan sem. Cras et cursus ligula. Cras porta ultrices turpis eu gravida. Duis sed lacus imperdiet, convallis est in, molestie libero. Nunc laoreet dolor tellus, eget sollicitudin nulla luctus tincidunt. Sed id mauris blandit, congue purus eget, sodales lorem. Aenean hendrerit lectus ac enim fermentum aliquam. Vivamus sem est, aliquet et ultricies ac, sollicitudin at elit.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="row picture-new">
            <div class="pic col">
                <img src="~/Upload/bg/bg.png" alt="" />
