        </div>
        <hr />
        <div class="row action">
            <div class="col like">
                <button><i id="hearts" class='bx bxs-heart-circle' style='color:#808080'></i></button>
            </div>
            <div class="col comment">
                <button><i class='bx bxs-message' style='color:#808080'></i></button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <hr />
        @*Vong lap comment*@
        <div class="row comment-gene items4">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="avatar-sm-usr"><img src="~/Upload/Team/Haru.jpg" alt="Alternate Text" />Haru(UserName)</div> @*Usr img, usr name*@
            </div>
            <div class="row message-box dummy">
                <p>
                    Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Phasellus hendrerit orci eget diam fermentum, eu fringilla odio  Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Phasellus hendrerit orci eget diam fermentum, eu fringilla odio lobortis. Donec lacinia  Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Phasellus hendrerit orci eget diam fermentum, eu fringilla odio lobortis. Donec lacinia lobortis. Donec lacinia fermentum cursus. Aliquam hendrerit pellentesque ligula vel scelerisque. Nam auctor risus quis lacus dignissim, sit amet porttitor libero pretium. Aenean viverra orci quam, at fringilla tellus viverra quis. Praesent convallis non sapien quis ullamcorper. Etiam sit amet justo sed erat vehicula condimentum. Quisque vel dignissim odio, eget convallis nunc.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        @*Vong lap comment*@
        <button class="LoadMore4">View more comment</button>
        <div class="row comment-box">
            <div class="text-comment">
                <form>
                    <div class="avatar-sm"><img src="~/Upload/Team/Hung.jpg" alt="Alternate Text" /></div> @*thang nao dang nhap thi la hinh cua thang do*@
                    <input type="text" value="" placeholder="Write comment...." />
                    <button><i class='bx bxs-send' style='color:#808080'></i></button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    @*vong lap bai viet*@

</div>

<script>
    $readMoreJS.init({
        target: '.dummy p',
        numOfWords: 70,
        toggle: true,                 // If true, user can toggle between 'read more' and 'read less'
        moreLink: '<span style="color:black;font-weight:bolder;">More</span>',
        lessLink: '<span style="color:black;font-weight:bolder;">Less</span>'
    });

    


    var hs = document.getElementById('hearts');
    $('.like button').click(function () {
        if (hs.style.color == 'red') 
        {
           hs.style.color = '#808080';
        } 
        else
        {
            hs.style.color = 'red';
        } 
    });

    $(".items4").slice(0, 1).show();
    $(".LoadMore4").on("click", function () {
        $(".items4:hidden").slice(0, 1).show();
        if ($(".items4:hidden").length == 0) {
            $(".LoadMore4").fadeOut();
        }
    });

</script>

